<h2 id="search-grad">Search gradients</h2>
<p>Usually when working on <strong>Evolution Strategy</strong> methods, we select some candidate solutions, which gererate better fitness values than the other ones, and produce the next generation from them. This means, majority of points have been wasted since they may contain some useful information.</p>

<p>To ultilize the use of discarded solutions, the <strong>NES</strong> uses <strong>search gradients</strong>.</p>

